1
00:00:03,260 --> 00:00:04,660
You!

2
00:00:06,198 --> 00:00:08,042
You!

3
00:00:08,042 --> 00:00:10,001
I wanted to see you.

4
00:00:12,121 --> 00:00:13,488
Good morning.

5
00:00:13,488 --> 00:00:15,148
"Good?"

6
00:00:15,148 --> 00:00:18,574
Do I seem "good" to you?

7
00:00:20,738 --> 00:00:22,138
Because of you...

8
00:00:22,138 --> 00:00:25,798
I had to write my first letter of explanation because of you.

9
00:00:25,798 --> 00:00:27,985
Do you know? Because of you!

10
00:00:27,985 --> 00:00:29,312
Because of a jerk like you!

11
00:00:29,312 --> 00:00:30,956
Because of you, who is not even a student here!

12
00:00:30,956 --> 00:00:33,830
Because of you! Because of you!

13
00:00:38,038 --> 00:00:39,406
It's because of you.

14
00:00:39,406 --> 00:00:41,791
I missed it because of you.

15
00:00:41,791 --> 00:00:44,277
You were too drunk.

16
00:00:44,277 --> 00:00:47,679
Even so, if I were Kim Yeon Du...

17
00:00:50,492 --> 00:00:54,569
Jerks like you should be banned from entering the campus.

18
00:00:54,569 --> 00:00:57,157
One rotten apple spoils the barrel.

19
00:00:57,157 --> 00:01:00,017
You even broke one of our doors.

20
00:01:00,017 --> 00:01:02,627
Hey. Are you listening to me?

21
00:01:02,627 --> 00:01:04,447
Do you understand?

22
00:01:04,447 --> 00:01:05,507
Because of you...

23
00:01:05,507 --> 00:01:07,087
You messed up my life!

24
00:01:07,087 --> 00:01:08,166
You should say thanks to him.

25
00:01:08,166 --> 00:01:09,811
Exactly, thank—

26
00:01:09,811 --> 00:01:11,387
What?

27
00:01:14,425 --> 00:01:17,477
I thought you'd be grateful.

28
00:01:18,170 --> 00:01:21,937
Grateful? Me?

29
00:01:21,937 --> 00:01:23,747
To him?

30
00:01:26,018 --> 00:01:28,368
Think about it.

31
00:01:28,368 --> 00:01:34,731
A business student was locked up and fainted in a darkroom which is your responsibility.

32
00:01:35,667 --> 00:01:41,122
It wouldn't have ended with a letter of explanation.

33
00:01:41,122 --> 00:01:41,852
Excuse me.

34
00:01:41,863 --> 00:01:44,295
A broken doorknob

35
00:01:44,295 --> 00:01:47,790
is not as important as saving someone.

36
00:01:50,110 --> 00:01:53,375
Ye Seok, what I mean is...

37
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:05,347
Well... Ji Hyeon Ho?

38
00:02:06,818 --> 00:02:08,044
I...

39
00:02:08,044 --> 00:02:10,780
I guess I was confused.

40
00:02:10,780 --> 00:02:12,856
I'm sorry.

41
00:02:12,856 --> 00:02:16,208
Well, have fun with your club activity.

42
00:02:16,208 --> 00:02:16,870
I have to go.

43
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:18,221
The professor is looking for me.

44
00:02:18,221 --> 00:02:19,147
Hello?

45
00:02:19,147 --> 00:02:20,715
I'm holding it upside down.

46
00:02:20,715 --> 00:02:22,391
Bye.

47
00:02:24,188 --> 00:02:25,767
Excuse me.

48
00:02:30,784 --> 00:02:32,818
Why did you help me?

49
00:02:33,512 --> 00:02:36,839
Are we close enough to help each other?

50
00:02:37,891 --> 00:02:38,834
I thought I could help.

51
00:02:38,834 --> 00:02:41,026
That's what I'm saying...

52
00:02:41,026 --> 00:02:43,955
Are we helping each other now because we can?

53
00:02:47,718 --> 00:02:49,443
I'm not sure.

54
00:02:50,179 --> 00:02:53,172
I don't know what terms we're on,

55
00:02:53,891 --> 00:02:55,575
but...

56
00:02:55,575 --> 00:02:59,426
That's one thing and this is another.

57
00:03:07,354 --> 00:03:09,438
What is he talking about?

58
00:03:13,985 --> 00:03:18,740
[Best Mistake 3]

59
00:03:30,076 --> 00:03:33,810
[Hwayang Festival preparation: Life4cuts]
[Booth survey: Do Ye Seok]

60
00:03:43,090 --> 00:03:45,642
For the upcoming festival,

61
00:03:45,642 --> 00:03:48,311
as a photography club, we will prepare a Life4cuts booth.

62
00:03:48,311 --> 00:03:52,232
Hwayang University Students, you'll be in charge because it's your school's festival.

63
00:03:52,232 --> 00:03:54,042
That's all for today.

64
00:03:54,042 --> 00:03:56,368
Good job.

65
00:03:56,368 --> 00:03:58,729
Bye.

66
00:04:15,943 --> 00:04:17,740
Jin Se Hui.

67
00:04:20,994 --> 00:04:23,053
Let's talk briefly.

68
00:04:37,869 --> 00:04:40,195
Yeon Du.

69
00:04:40,195 --> 00:04:42,314
Yes, Senior?

70
00:04:42,314 --> 00:04:45,583
Do you want to take photos with me?

71
00:04:45,583 --> 00:04:47,328
Pardon?

72
00:04:50,132 --> 00:04:53,034
You know the Life4cuts booth we're preparing for the festival.

73
00:04:53,034 --> 00:04:55,278
It has many different frames.

74
00:04:55,278 --> 00:04:58,823
I thought it'd be better to try all of them and pick the best ones.

75
00:05:00,258 --> 00:05:03,202
So I was wondering if you were free to come with me today.

76
00:05:04,204 --> 00:05:06,956
Sure, let's go.

77
00:05:15,173 --> 00:05:16,524
What's up?

78
00:05:16,524 --> 00:05:18,293
I thought you would never want to see me again.

79
00:05:18,293 --> 00:05:19,369
Right.

80
00:05:19,369 --> 00:05:23,446
I thought I'd never see you again, but I need to check something.

81
00:05:23,446 --> 00:05:25,457
Check?

82
00:05:25,457 --> 00:05:29,145
Kim Yeon Du was locked up in the darkroom at your school a few days ago.

83
00:05:29,145 --> 00:05:32,738
On the day you and I ran into each other at the campus.

84
00:05:32,738 --> 00:05:34,642
Remember?

85
00:05:39,473 --> 00:05:42,875
Kim Yeon Du said it was an accident,

86
00:05:42,875 --> 00:05:49,394
but I think it was an incident that was very intentionally planned.

87
00:05:51,652 --> 00:05:54,578
Do you think I did it?

88
00:05:56,498 --> 00:05:59,725
Do you think I locked Kim Yeon Du in the darkroom?

89
00:05:59,725 --> 00:06:01,685
You didn't?

90
00:06:01,685 --> 00:06:04,772
With running into me by chance one time, you're going too far.

91
00:06:04,772 --> 00:06:07,750
Don't try to frame me like this.

92
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:09,927
You don't even have evidence.

93
00:06:10,712 --> 00:06:15,146
By chance? Was it really by chance?

94
00:06:15,146 --> 00:06:17,460
Do you like Kim Yeon Du so much?

95
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:19,012
What on earth do you like about her?

96
00:06:19,012 --> 00:06:21,881
Do you like how she pretends to be nice and naive?

97
00:06:21,881 --> 00:06:24,533
Do you like how she smiles at everyone?

98
00:06:24,533 --> 00:06:26,239
What do you like about her?

99
00:06:26,239 --> 00:06:27,912
Hey.

100
00:06:28,622 --> 00:06:32,424
Don't talk about her that way.

101
00:06:32,424 --> 00:06:34,743
How dare you...

102
00:06:38,924 --> 00:06:40,308
Fine.

103
00:06:40,308 --> 00:06:43,569
Let's say it was by chance that we ran into each other.

104
00:06:44,179 --> 00:06:47,473
But this has happened before.

105
00:06:47,473 --> 00:06:50,910
At the outing and now this.

106
00:06:50,910 --> 00:06:53,779
You're always there when something happens to Kim Yeon Du.

107
00:06:53,779 --> 00:06:56,248
Are you saying that's a coincidence?

108
00:06:59,177 --> 00:07:00,970
Just say it.

109
00:07:00,970 --> 00:07:01,955
Say what?

110
00:07:01,955 --> 00:07:05,100
Say what you really want to say.

111
00:07:05,100 --> 00:07:07,160
"Jin Se Hui locked you in the darkroom."

112
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:09,820
"She is the worst person so don't hang out with her."

113
00:07:09,820 --> 00:07:13,008
Go to Kim Yeon Du and tell her that.

114
00:07:13,008 --> 00:07:15,367
Why don't you tell her that?

115
00:07:19,798 --> 00:07:23,580
It's because you have some feelings for me—

116
00:07:26,663 --> 00:07:29,164
Don't make me laugh.

117
00:07:29,164 --> 00:07:33,193
You're totally wrong.

118
00:07:34,337 --> 00:07:38,774
I haven't said anything for her sake, not for you.

119
00:07:38,774 --> 00:07:43,553
She thinks you're a good person.

120
00:07:43,553 --> 00:07:46,231
I don't want to break her heart.

121
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:55,162
So stop kidding yourself but go to Kim Yeon Du and apologize.

122
00:07:59,162 --> 00:08:01,597
I won't wait for long.

123
00:08:04,766 --> 00:08:06,777
Kim Yeon Du...

124
00:08:15,962 --> 00:08:17,730
Senior!

125
00:08:20,066 --> 00:08:22,142
Hi, you're here.

126
00:08:22,142 --> 00:08:24,220
I'm sorry I'm late.

127
00:08:24,220 --> 00:08:25,828
I saw the time wrong.

128
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:28,587
It's okay. I haven't been waiting long.

129
00:08:30,393 --> 00:08:33,320
Oh? This shirt...

130
00:08:34,998 --> 00:08:37,139
Do you remember it?

131
00:08:37,139 --> 00:08:40,746
Of course, how could I forget?

132
00:08:41,546 --> 00:08:45,705
Senior Ye Seok, did you wear this shirt on purpose?

133
00:08:45,705 --> 00:08:48,177
To remind me of my embarrassing past?

134
00:08:48,177 --> 00:08:51,785
It may be embarrassing to you, but not to me.

135
00:08:51,785 --> 00:08:53,449
Pardon?

136
00:08:53,449 --> 00:08:55,075
Let's go.

137
00:08:55,994 --> 00:08:57,536
Yes.

138
00:09:03,635 --> 00:09:06,612
This is my favorite shirt.

139
00:09:45,927 --> 00:09:50,300
[Life4cuts SELF STUDIO]

140
00:09:50,300 --> 00:09:54,810
♫ There are so many songs about love in the world ♫

141
00:09:54,810 --> 00:09:59,230
♫ Then let's sing without that ♫

142
00:09:59,230 --> 00:10:00,020
♫ There is so much happiness in the world that you can't see well ♫

143
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:03,700
This one is cute.
♫ There is so much happiness in the world that you can't see well ♫

144
00:10:03,700 --> 00:10:08,110
♫ I want to find something happier than love ♫

145
00:10:08,900 --> 00:10:13,930
♫ When everything becomes obvious and everything becomes hate ♫

146
00:10:13,930 --> 00:10:16,540
Try this on.

147
00:10:16,540 --> 00:10:19,613
I think it'll look good on you.

148
00:10:19,613 --> 00:10:20,720
No, thanks.

149
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:23,271
Come on. Just this once.

150
00:10:23,271 --> 00:10:26,620
Please? I chose it for you.

151
00:10:26,620 --> 00:10:28,490
♫ I'm crazy about famous love songs ♫

152
00:10:28,498 --> 00:10:30,960
Just this once, please. Okay?

153
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:35,060
♫ When I am not interested ♫

154
00:10:42,091 --> 00:10:45,420
It looks good on you. You look like a rabbit.

155
00:10:50,367 --> 00:10:51,909
Look.

156
00:10:53,962 --> 00:10:55,196
[Life4cuts]

157
00:10:55,196 --> 00:10:59,170
I picked out some cute frames on the Life4cuts app.

158
00:10:59,170 --> 00:11:03,890
♫ The two of us that seems 100 percent close and perfect ♫

159
00:11:03,890 --> 00:11:06,015
Let's try this one first.

160
00:11:06,015 --> 00:11:08,676
Okay.
♫ 0 percent in one day ♫

161
00:11:08,676 --> 00:11:12,210
It worked.
♫ 0 percent in one day ♫

162
00:11:12,210 --> 00:11:16,330
♫ 100 percent between the two of us ♫

163
00:11:16,330 --> 00:11:21,020
♫ It's getting perfect again ♫

164
00:11:21,020 --> 00:11:28,850
♫ Like being possessed by something ♫

165
00:11:28,850 --> 00:11:33,090
♫ It's getting perfect again ♫

166
00:11:33,090 --> 00:11:37,350
♫ Like it lasts only for a moment ♫

167
00:11:37,350 --> 00:11:40,580
♫ I really wanna like you ♫

168
00:11:44,229 --> 00:11:46,271
Dae Yeong.

169
00:11:46,271 --> 00:11:48,832
Oh? Seol.

170
00:11:49,818 --> 00:11:51,568
Hi.

171
00:11:52,537 --> 00:11:55,380
What brought you here at this hour?

172
00:11:56,141 --> 00:11:58,800
I have a class nearby.

173
00:12:00,328 --> 00:12:03,927
Are you here to see me?

174
00:12:05,250 --> 00:12:06,550
Yes.

175
00:12:06,550 --> 00:12:07,927
Pardon?

176
00:12:07,927 --> 00:12:09,786
Are you here to see me?

177
00:12:13,742 --> 00:12:16,568
Do you want to use me again?

178
00:12:16,568 --> 00:12:17,903
No.

179
00:12:17,903 --> 00:12:20,756
I won't do that anymore.

180
00:12:22,926 --> 00:12:25,427
That's why I'm here to tell you.

181
00:12:29,174 --> 00:12:31,208
That means...

182
00:12:31,843 --> 00:12:33,652
That's right.

183
00:12:33,652 --> 00:12:37,285
He... and I decided to go out.

184
00:12:46,232 --> 00:12:49,134
Thank you for liking me.

185
00:12:49,134 --> 00:12:53,578
And it was only for a short time,

186
00:12:53,578 --> 00:12:55,582
but I'm sorry for using you.

187
00:12:58,495 --> 00:12:59,751
Well, that's because I—

188
00:12:59,751 --> 00:13:01,730
No.

189
00:13:01,730 --> 00:13:05,710
I shouldn't have done that even though you allowed it.

190
00:13:07,253 --> 00:13:12,779
That wasn't fair to him or to you.

191
00:13:13,676 --> 00:13:15,585
I'm sorry.

192
00:13:27,649 --> 00:13:30,916
The truth is I was expecting it.

193
00:13:31,961 --> 00:13:36,946
I've only seen him a few times, but I could see it.

194
00:13:37,742 --> 00:13:40,520
I could see how much he liked you.

195
00:13:44,885 --> 00:13:47,640
I want you both to be happy.

196
00:13:50,964 --> 00:13:55,805
Don't make me regret giving up my love for you.

197
00:14:29,979 --> 00:14:34,155
Wow! The weather is nice.

198
00:14:34,155 --> 00:14:36,824
It is. It's really nice.

199
00:14:36,824 --> 00:14:39,771
I would've asked him out already if he hadn't been here.

200
00:14:39,771 --> 00:14:40,905
Oh, right.

201
00:14:40,905 --> 00:14:45,175
He should take a hint and leave us alone by now.

202
00:14:45,175 --> 00:14:46,444
Kang Ah Hun.

203
00:14:46,444 --> 00:14:48,945
How oblivious he is.

204
00:14:56,613 --> 00:14:58,781
An Yu Na?

205
00:14:58,781 --> 00:15:00,749
Baek Se Chan?

206
00:15:00,749 --> 00:15:03,734
It's been a while. How have you been?

207
00:15:03,734 --> 00:15:05,462
I called you.

208
00:15:05,462 --> 00:15:07,064
But you didn't answer my call.

209
00:15:07,064 --> 00:15:09,768
Why would I answer your call?

210
00:15:09,768 --> 00:15:13,010
We're not close enough to call each other.

211
00:15:23,940 --> 00:15:27,214
Who is this? Your boyfriend?

212
00:15:27,214 --> 00:15:29,702
What do you mean, "Boyfriend?"

213
00:15:29,702 --> 00:15:32,690
She doesn't have a boyfriend.

214
00:15:36,719 --> 00:15:40,420
Then... Do you want to grab a bite with me some time?

215
00:15:40,420 --> 00:15:42,047
There's a new place—

216
00:15:42,047 --> 00:15:43,801
Why would I grab a bite with you—

217
00:15:43,801 --> 00:15:46,650
She won't be available that day.

218
00:15:55,595 --> 00:15:57,739
Whenever that might be.

219
00:15:59,467 --> 00:16:01,927
Because I'll be with her.

220
00:16:28,429 --> 00:16:31,055
You're popular, An Yu Na.

221
00:16:31,055 --> 00:16:33,690
I didn't even mention when.

222
00:16:46,155 --> 00:16:50,256
Sorry. You were surprised, right?

223
00:16:50,256 --> 00:16:52,414
Did you...

224
00:16:52,414 --> 00:16:55,697
Did you just confess your feelings for me?

225
00:16:55,697 --> 00:16:57,416
Yes.

226
00:16:59,077 --> 00:17:00,810
Hey.

227
00:17:00,810 --> 00:17:05,497
I liked you first but why do you confess to me first?

228
00:17:05,497 --> 00:17:08,418
That's cheating.

229
00:17:08,418 --> 00:17:11,004
It's not cheating.

230
00:17:18,729 --> 00:17:20,680
No!

231
00:17:29,974 --> 00:17:34,553
They were all cute, but I think the frames we took together are the best.

232
00:17:34,553 --> 00:17:38,570
I think everyone will like them because they're simple and neat.

233
00:17:39,667 --> 00:17:41,043
Love is all about timing.

234
00:17:41,043 --> 00:17:42,726
No matter how much you love her,

235
00:17:42,726 --> 00:17:45,600
it'll be futile if you miss the timing.

236
00:17:47,770 --> 00:17:49,960
[21st Seoul International Culinary Competition Application Form]

237
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:51,962
0035...
[Name: Ji Hyeon Ho]

238
00:17:51,962 --> 00:17:54,214
5888.

239
00:17:54,974 --> 00:17:57,762
The address is correct.

240
00:17:57,762 --> 00:18:00,553
My cooking license number?

241
00:18:01,172 --> 00:18:03,248
Where did I put the license?

242
00:18:09,055 --> 00:18:11,339
This is Yeon Du's.

243
00:18:12,141 --> 00:18:14,134
Why is this here?

244
00:18:21,834 --> 00:18:24,302
Oh, that day...

245
00:18:25,029 --> 00:18:26,980
It's fine.

246
00:18:26,980 --> 00:18:27,803
I'll give it back to her.

247
00:18:27,803 --> 00:18:31,190
It'll be a chance to see her again.

248
00:18:31,994 --> 00:18:34,070
I hope she doesn't mind me reading it.

249
00:18:37,959 --> 00:18:39,451
It's a picture of me.

250
00:18:39,451 --> 00:18:41,610
When did she take this?

251
00:18:44,841 --> 00:18:47,100
What's this?

252
00:18:55,803 --> 00:18:58,845
Thank you for walking me home, Senior.

253
00:18:58,845 --> 00:19:00,798
I'll go inside.

254
00:19:00,798 --> 00:19:03,390
Bye. Get home safely.

255
00:19:03,390 --> 00:19:05,143
Wait.

256
00:19:08,406 --> 00:19:10,565
Wait, Yeon Du.

257
00:19:11,442 --> 00:19:12,884
Yes?

258
00:19:23,012 --> 00:19:26,039
[20st Seoul International Culinary Competition Application Form]
[Name: Ji Hyeon Ho]

259
00:19:26,039 --> 00:19:29,550
This is my application form from last year.

260
00:19:31,345 --> 00:19:33,713
Why does Yeon Du have this?

261
00:19:42,039 --> 00:19:43,765
Don't go.

262
00:19:45,084 --> 00:19:46,626
Pardon?

263
00:19:47,445 --> 00:19:50,396
I like you, Yeon Du.

264
00:19:58,831 --> 00:20:04,324
So don't go... to Ji Hyeon Ho.

265
00:20:22,010 --> 00:20:23,700
♫ Spread towards you ♫

266
00:20:23,700 --> 00:20:27,116
[Best Mistake 3]

267
00:20:27,116 --> 00:20:31,313
I picked out some cute frames on the Life4cuts app.

268
00:20:31,313 --> 00:20:34,490
Let's try this one first.

269
00:20:35,550 --> 00:20:39,330
♫ I bet it all, I like a fire ♫

270
00:20:39,330 --> 00:20:42,680
♫ Like a fire ♫

271
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:44,960
♫ You are like the midday sun ♫

272
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:47,280
♫ Even if everything disappears like the wind ♫

